196
00:17:18,340 --> 00:17:20,740
It's like this coin.

197
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:24,800
If you never give this a chance, you'll never know the answer.

198
00:17:33,230 --> 00:17:36,450
Even if it's the opposite, we can face it together.

199
00:17:36,450 --> 00:17:39,500
It's just like how we face divorce cases together.

200
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:59,640
Well then, don't throw it just yet.

201
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:02,770
That way, I won't have to receive an answer I don't want to know.

202
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:16,450
I'm sorry. I want to calm down a bit by myself.

203
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,920
Where is Big Brother Yuki?

204
00:18:44,650 --> 00:18:46,570
Dad.

205
00:18:50,410 --> 00:18:52,640
Big Brother Yuki...

206
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:54,960
