208
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:04,040
Dad, you can't lie. Otherwise, I'll hate you.

209
00:19:11,180 --> 00:19:16,130
Ling Ling, I want to ask you...

210
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:21,880
One day, if I threw away your favorite toys and books,

211
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,660
how would you feel?

212
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:25,740
Well, it would depend on whether I needed them or not.

213
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:28,800
If I already finished reading those books,

214
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:32,570
even if you threw them away, I wouldn't be upset.

215
00:19:32,570 --> 00:19:35,580
But... do you understand?

216
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:39,260
Big Brother Yuki moved around

217
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:41,520
