249
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,980
I'm sorry.

250
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:08,600
I was too impulsive today.

251
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,900
Can you forgive me?

252
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:23,660
